* An increase in finance costs arising from higher working capital borrowings to support expanded operations and inventory requirements;
* Compression in operating margins, with EBITDA margin declining from 5.83% in Fiscal 2024 to 4.21% in Fiscal 2025; and
* Reduced profitability, with PAT decreasing from ₹2,270.41 lakhs in Fiscal 2024 to ₹1,090.63 lakhs in Fiscal 2025.
